非推奨のAPI

コンテンツ

  • 非推奨のクラス
  • 非推奨のメソッド
  • 非推奨のクラス 
    クラスと説明
    org.sxb.plugin.auth.AccessTokenBuilder
    org.sxb.core.JdkVersion
    as of Spring 4.2.1, in favor of direct checks for the desired JDK API variants via reflection
    org.sxb.data.redis.connection.jedis.JedisUtils
    org.sxb.data.redis.connection.PoolConfig
    use GenericObjectPoolConfig instead. Will be removed in 1.4.
  • 非推奨のメソッド 
    メソッドと説明
    org.sxb.data.redis.connection.DefaultStringRedisConnection.bgWriteAof()
    As of 1.3, use DefaultStringRedisConnection.bgReWriteAof().
    org.sxb.convert.sp.GenericTypeResolver.getTargetType(MethodParameter)
    as of Spring 4.0, use MethodParameter.getGenericParameterType()
    org.sxb.convert.sp.GenericTypeResolver.getTypeVariableMap(Class<?>)
    as of Spring 4.0 in favor of ResolvableType
    org.sxb.convert.sp.GenericTypeResolver.resolveType(Type, Map<TypeVariable, Type>)
    as of Spring 4.0 in favor of ResolvableType
    org.sxb.render.JspRender.setSupportActiveRecord(boolean)
    org.sxb.test.jspec.Inflector.shortName(String)
    Use clazz.getSimpleName() instead of Inflector.shortName(clazz.getName()).
